Please, do not muddy the issue.
We were talking about a standalone tool which is managing compilation
(not even a compiler!)
There is no ambiguity about linkage here, for the good reason that
there is nothing to link to.

Or will you tell me that using gnu make forces me to put all my software
under the GPL!

